title: Great Location! Two Adjacent Parcels 1211 W. Washington
text:
Great Location! Two Adjacent Parcels 1211 W. Washington ad date: 10/10/2015 
Two Adjacent Parcels 1211 W. Washington Blvd., Crescent City, CA Two adjacent parcels: 116-270-32 is 1.87 acres and runs parallel to Hwy 101 access ramp from Washington Blvd. 116-263-27 is 1.65 acres and is off Parkway. There is a driveway easement on 116-263-27 to an adjacent property that can be used to view the subject property. All permits, requirements and zoning need to be confirmed with Del Norte County. No. 1500386 $150,000
